#🧩 Responsive Web Design & Development Assignment

## 💻 Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (vanilla)
- PHP
- MySQL (with SQL stored in `/sql/database.sql`)

---

## 📁 Project Structure

/RWDD-Assignment/
│
├── index.html                  ← Main homepage
├── contact.php                 ← PHP page with form/database
├── config.php                  ← Database connection file
│
├── /assets/
│   ├── /css/
│   │   ├── style.css           ← Global styles
│   │   └── contact.css         ← (Optional) page-specific styles
│   ├── /js/
│   │   ├── main.js             ← Shared JS
│   │   └── contact.js          ← (Optional) page-specific JS
│   └── /images/                ← Image assets
│
├── /includes/
│   ├── header.php              ← Shared header
│   └── footer.php              ← Shared footer
│
├── /sql/
│   └── database.sql            ← Exported MySQL database
│
├── README.md                   ← This file
└── .gitignore                  ← Files to ignore when pushing
